<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
      <body>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Early Christian Writings</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/fstyles.css">
    <style>
    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
        background: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  margin: 20px 0;
  padding: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  max-width: 100%; /* Ensure cards don't exceed container width */
  width: 95%; /* Adjust this value to control card width */
    }

    .card.collapsed {
      padding: 10px 20px;
    }

    .card.collapsed .card-content {
      display: none;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    .card em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: #777;
    }

    .card-category {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #3498db;
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Flexbox Layout for Cards */
    .card-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 20px; /* Space between cards */
    }
  </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="announcement-banner" class="banner-container">
      <div class="banner-text"> <a href="index.html" class="banner-link">BACK
          TO MAIN SITE</a> </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="toc">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#introduction">Introduction</a></li>
        <li><a href="#1st-century">1st Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#late-1st-early-2nd-century">Late 1st–Early 2nd Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#early-2nd-century">Early 2nd Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#mid-2nd-century">Mid-2nd Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#late-2nd-century">Late 2nd Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#late-2nd-early-3rd-century">Late 2nd–Early 3rd Century</a></li>
        <li><a href="#early-3rd-century">Early 3rd Century</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="centre_me">Early Christian Writings (Pre-325 AD)</h1>
      <!-- 1st Century -->
      <h1 id="1st-century">1st Century</h1>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card collapsed" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
          <h3>The New Testament</h3>
          <div class="card-content"> <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100"

              alt="New Testament">
            <p><em>Various authors, 1st century</em></p>
            <p>The foundational texts of Christianity, including the Gospels,
              Acts, Epistles, and Revelation.</p>
            <p class="card-category">Category: Scripture</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Late 1st–Early 2nd Century -->
      <h1 id="late-1st-early-2nd-century">Late 1st–Early 2nd Century</h1>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card collapsed" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
          <h3>The Didache</h3>
          <div class="card-content"> <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100"

              alt="Didache">
            <p><em>Anonymous, late 1st–early 2nd century</em></p>
            <p>A manual of Christian ethics, worship, and church order, often
              referred to as "The Teaching of the Twelve Apostles."</p>
            <p class="card-category">Category: Church Manual</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card collapsed" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
          <h3>The Epistle of Barnabas</h3>
          <div class="card-content"> <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100"

              alt="Epistle of Barnabas">
            <p><em>Anonymous, early 2nd century</em></p>
            <p>A theological treatise emphasizing the fulfillment of Old
              Testament prophecies in Christ.</p>
            <p class="card-category">Category: Theology</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Early 2nd Century -->
      <h1 id="early-2nd-century">Early 2nd Century</h1>
      <div class="card-container">
        <div class="card collapsed" onclick="toggleCard(this)">
          <h3>Pliny the Younger (Epistles 10.96)</h3>
          <div class="card-content"> <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/100"

              alt="Pliny the Younger">
            <p><em>Pliny the Younger, c. 112 AD</em></p>
            <p>A Roman governor’s letter describing early Christian worship
              practices, including hymn-singing and communal meals.</p>
            <p class="card-category">Category: Historical Account</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Conclusion -->
      <h1 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h1>
      <div class="ds-markdown ds-markdown--block" style="--ds-md-zoom: 1.143;">
        <p>This list provides a comprehensive overview of early Christian
          writings, showcasing the rich theological and liturgical traditions of
          the Church Fathers before 325 AD.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
    // Function to toggle card expansion
    function toggleCard(card) {
      card.classList.toggle("collapsed");
    }
  </script>
  </body>
</html>
